description: [``botocore``] Changes include: new GetVirtualMachineApi to fetch a single user's VM, improving ListVirtualMachines to fetch filtered VMs as well as all VMs, and improving GetGatewayApi to now also return the gateway's MaintenanceStartTime.
[``botocore``] This release adds the support for VPC-ENI based connectivity for private devices on AWS Device Farm.
[``botocore``] Added support for S3 Event Notifications for Catalog Target Crawlers.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for the Identity Store CLI Reference.
